\c 6
\s Ukwanda kobubi babantu
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi abantu sebeqala ukwanda ebusweni bomhlaba, basebezalelwa amadodakazi,
\v 2 amadodana kaNkulunkulu ebona amadodakazi abantu ukuthi wona ayemahle; asezithathela abafazi kuwo wonke awakhethayo\x + Dute. 7.3,4.\x*.
\v 3 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi: UMoya wami kawuyikulwisana lomuntu njalonjalo\x + Gal. 5.16,17.\x*, ngoba laye eyinyama\x + Hlab. 78.39.\x*; kodwa izinsuku zakhe zizakuba yiminyaka elikhulu lamatshumi amabili.
\v 4 Iziqhwaga zazisemhlabeni ngalezonsuku; lemva kwalokho-ke, lapho amadodana kaNkulunkulu esengenile emadodakazini abantu, asewazalela \add abantwana\add*. Wona ayengamaqhawe asendulo, engamadoda alebizo.
\p
\v 5 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasibona ukuthi ububi bomuntu bukhulu emhlabeni, lokuthi konke ukuceba kwemicabango\f + \fk imicabango: \fl Ibala lesiHebheru litsho lenjongo leziloyiso.\f* yenhliziyo yakhe kwakukubi kuphela usuku lonke\x + 8.21. Jobe 14.4; 15.14. Hlab. 51.5. Jer. 17.9. Mat. 15.19. Roma 3.23.\x*.
\v 6 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasizisola\x + 1 Sam. 15.11. 2 Sam. 24.16. Jow. 2.13. Nani 23.19. 1 Sam. 15.29. Gen. 18.30. Isa. 1.14; 43.24.\x* ngokuthi yayimenzile umuntu emhlabeni, yasidabuka enhliziyweni yayo\x + Isa. 63.10. Efe. 4.30.\x*.
\v 7 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi: Ngizamchitha umuntu engamdalayo ngimsuse ebusweni bomhlaba, kusukela emuntwini kusiya enyamazaneni, kuze kube kokuhuquzelayo, lenyonini zamazulu; ngoba ngiyazisola ukuthi ngikwenzile.
\v 8 Kodwa uNowa wazuza umusa emehlweni eN\nd kosi\x + 19.19. Eks. 33.12,13,16,17. Luka 1.30. Seb. 7.46.\x*\nd*.
\s UNowa wenza umkhumbi
\p
\v 9 Lezi yizizukulwana zikaNowa. UNowa wayeyindoda elungileyo\x + Hez. 14.14,20. 2 Pet. 2.5.\x* epheleleyo\f + \fk epheleleyo: \fl kumbe, \fq eqotho.\f* esizukulwaneni sakhe; uNowa wahamba loNkulunkulu\x + 5.22,24.\x*.
\v 10 UNowa wasezala amadodana amathathu, uShemu, uHamu loJafethi.
\v 11 Umhlaba wonakaliswa-ke phambi kukaNkulunkulu\x + 7.1; 10.9; 13.13. Luka 1.6. Roma 2.13; 3.19.\x*, lomhlaba wagcwaliswa ngobudlwangudlwangu\x + Hez. 8.17; 9.9; 28.16.\x*.
\v 12 UNkulunkulu wasebona umhlaba\x + 18.21. Hlab. 14.2; 53.2,3.\x*, khangela-ke wonakalisiwe, ngoba yonke inyama yonakalise indlela yayo emhlabeni.
\v 13 UNkulunkulu wasesithi kuNowa: Ukuphela kwayo yonke inyama sekuze phambi kwami\x + Hez. 7.2,3,6.\x*, ngoba umhlaba ugcwele ubudlwangudlwangu ngenxa yabo; khangela-ke, ngizabachitha kanye lomhlaba.
\v 14 Zakhele umkhumbi ngezigodo \w zegofere\w**, wenze izigaba\f + \fk izigaba: \fl kumbe, \fq izidleke.\f* phakathi komkhumbi, uwuhuqe ngengcino ngaphakathi langaphandle.
\v 15 Nansi indlela ozawenza ngayo; ingalo ezingamakhulu amathathu yibude bomkhumbi, ingalo ezingamatshumi amahlanu yibubanzi bawo, ingalo ezingamatshumi amathathu yikuphakama kwawo.
\v 16 Iwindi uzalenza emkhunjini, uliqede libe yingalo kusukela phezulu, ufake umnyango womkhumbi ehlangothini lwawo, uwenze ube \add lesitezi\add* esaphansi, esesibili, lesesithathu.
\v 17 Mina-ke, khangela, ngizakwehlisela uzamcolo wamanzi phezu komhlaba, ukuchitha yonke inyama, okukuyo umoya wempilo, isuke ngaphansi kwamazulu. Konke okusemhlabeni kuzaphela.
\v 18 Kodwa ngizamisa isivumelwano sami lawe; njalo uzangena emkhunjini, wena lamadodana akho lomkakho labafazi bamadodana akho kanye lawe.
\v 19 Lakukho konke okuphilayo, kuyo yonke inyama, okubili kwakho konke, uzakuletha emkhunjini, u\add ku\add*londoloze kuphila lawe, kuzakuba ngokuduna lokusikazi;
\v 20 enyonini ngohlobo lwayo, lesifuyweni ngohlobo lwaso, lakukho konke okuhuquzelayo komhlaba ngohlobo lwakho, okubili kwakho kuzakuza kuwe\x + 2.19.\x*, u\add ku\add*londoloze kuphila.
\v 21 Lawe-ke, zithathele kukho konke ukudla okudliwayo, njalo ukubuthelele kuwe, futhi kuzakuba ngokwakho lokwazo okokudla.
\v 22 Wasekwenza uNowa\x + Heb. 11.7. Eks. 40.16.\x*; njengakho konke uNkulunkulu ayemlaye khona wenza njalo.
